types as causal variables subject to intervention analysis; (b) introducing a hybrid loss combining ICL, conditional mutual information minimization (to remove fake invariance), and language-supervised contrastive alignment; and (c) a prototype composition module that preserves invariance during recombination. This moves beyond black-box representations toward transparent, modular, and reusable visual knowledge.",
